      <div class="char-section">
        <h3 class="t-en">The Question This Chapter Must Answer</h3>
        <h3 class="t-id">Pertanyaan yang Harus Dijawab Bab Ini</h3>
        <p class="t-en">
          The question his chapter must answer is not whether he is capable. He
          is demonstrably capable. The question is what he is capable for: what,
          underneath the economy and the misdirection and the twenty generations
          of inherited name, Nero XXI is actually working toward.
        </p>
        <p class="t-id">
          Pertanyaan yang harus dijawab babnya bukan soal apakah ia mampu. Ia jelas mampu.
          Pertanyaannya: untuk apa ia mampu. Apa, di balik semua ekonomi dan pengalihan dan
          dua puluh generasi nama warisan, yang sebenarnya sedang ia kejar.
        </p>
      </div>

